<subSubSection pageId="15" pageNumber="141" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="15.[1428,2634,300,647]" pageId="15" pageNumber="141">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1429,1784,379,408]" pageId="15" pageNumber="141">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
CITES Appendix II. Classified as Endangered on the The [UCN Red List. Fully protected over most ofits range. Hunting and trade prohibited. Extremely rare, probably fewer than eight individuals have been trapped since 1928. Local trappers and animal dealers are aware of the species value and demandsforlive specimens have increased illegal trapping pressure, which mayjeopardize this rare species.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
